OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog patches soon
OL,6,Fclearing this morning. Otherwise all
OL,7,Fparts will have a dry day with some
OL,8,Flengthy spells of sunshine. Light and
OL,9,Fvariable winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fclear with some patchy frost. Clouding
OL,13,Fover from the south in the early hours
OL,14,Fwith a few showers breaking out.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FChance of a shower at first
OL,17,Fotherwise mainly dry and rather
OL,18,Fcloudy. A few bright spells breaking
OL,19,Fthrough along the north coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
